Sorry everyone, this is completely OT, but for some reason my emails to
Elaine aren't going through.

Elaine - Shipping to UK for 2 books is $6 economy (4-6 weeks) and $13 for
shipping that takes about a week. You can change the shipping amount before
you confirm payment with Paypal. I'll be at the conference until the 12th,
and won't have a chance to get to the post office before we leave, but if
you do place an order I'll try to get to it right away when we get back.
~Rue
